{"tid":2105874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"檢疫變逃疫 一名隔離檢疫男子青沙公路跳車被制服","createTime":"2020-07-13T02:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T09:59:04.000Z","uid":31314,"like":189,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"b98964406f1040bbcb823ecee5729a47150ebd5b","tid":2105874,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:51:25.000Z","msg":"今日(13日)清晨6時許，一輛載有3名接受隔離檢疫人士的小巴，沿青沙公路駛往火炭駿洋邨，駛至大圍近松嶺路，其中一名接受檢疫男子突然打開車尾太平門跳車逃走，司機見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n其後，數名警員接報趕至，其中一名便裝警員上前制止跳車漢時遇反抗，經一番糾纏終將其制服，他一度躺在路旁吸煙；便裝警身體感痛楚，跳車漢亦報稱受傷，兩人隨後由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n事件中出現一段小插曲，有記者路經見狀，即時上前訪攝，期間遭警員阻止及用手遮擋鏡頭，擾攘一番才讓記者離開。"},{"pid":"0869af2a70796db847471b9fab05ed882697a890","tid":2105874,"uid":39210,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:53:33.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdb53903c40baca1598f5800e817ee6103c80f3","tid":2105874,"uid":11960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"藍屍？"},{"pid":"9543f802ecd40229032c15d525498cdc4a0afcda","tid":2105874,"uid":3980,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:10:31.000Z","msg":"襲警+拒捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b954dd6ce7704894d2967f93110bcdaf921db68","tid":2105874,"uid":886,"like":105,"dislike":0,"score":105,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"經一番糾纏終將其制服，他一度躺在路旁吸煙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as